---
title: Chicken Steak & Twice-Cooked Rosemary Potatoes Take your cooking skills to the next level!
description: Time to unleash your inner chef! Tender chicken breast is seared to perfection, and is topped with a home-made garlic and dijon
compound butter. We think the real star of the show is the twice-cooked roast potatoes - don’t worry, we’ve given you all the tips
to achieve your crispiest roasties yet!
